#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the documentation for the &systemsettings; module that configures "
"mice and other pointing devices."
msgstr ""
"Hau da, saguak eta beste gailu erakusle batzuk konfiguratzeko "
"&systemsettings;(e)ko moduluaren dokumentazioa."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Systemsettings"
msgstr "Sistemaren ezarpenak"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "mouse"
msgstr "Sagua"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This module allows you to configure your pointing device. Your pointing "
#| "device may be a mouse, a track ball, a touch-pad, or another piece of "
#| "hardware that performs a similar function."
msgid ""
"This module allows you to configure your pointing device. Your pointing "
"device may be a mouse, a trackball, a touchpad, or another piece of hardware "
"that performs a similar function."
msgstr ""
"Modulu honek zure gailu erakuslea konfiguratzen uzten dizu. Zure gailu "
"erakuslea sagu bat, kontrol-bola bat, ukimen-sagu bat, edo funtzio bertsua "
"gauzatzen duen beste hardware pieza bat izan daiteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Orokorra"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left handed mouse"
msgstr "Ezkertiarrentzako sagua"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are left-handed, you may prefer to swap the functions of the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons "
"on your pointing device by checking this option. If your pointing device has "
"more than two buttons, only those that function as the <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons are affected. For "
"example, if you have a three-button mouse, the <mousebutton>middle</"
"mousebutton> button is unaffected."
msgstr ""
"Ezkertia bazara, aukera hau markatuz, zure gailu erakusleko "
"<mousebutton>ezker</mousebutton> eta <mousebutton>eskuin</mousebutton> "
"botoien funtzioa truka dezakezu. Zure gailu erakusleak bi botoi baino "
"gehiago baditu, <mousebutton>ezker</mousebutton> eta <mousebutton>eskuin</"
"mousebutton> botoi gisa dihardutenei eragingo die. Adibidez, hiru botoiko "
"sagu bat baduzu, <mousebutton>erdiko</mousebutton> botoiari ez dio eragiten."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press left and right buttons for middle-click"
msgstr "Sakatu ezker eta eskuin botoiak erdiko-klik egiteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this item if you don't have a &MMB;. You can press the left and right "
"mouse buttons at the same time to emulate middle-click."
msgstr ""
"Markatu elementu hori &MMB;rik ez baduzu. Saguaren ezker eta eskuin botoiak "
"aldi berean saka ditzakezu erdiko-klik emulatzeko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer speed"
msgstr "Erakuslearen abiadura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This option allows you to change the relationship between the distance "
#| "that the mouse pointer moves on the screen and the relative movement of "
#| "the physical device itself (which may be a mouse, track-ball, or some "
#| "other pointing device.)"
msgid ""
"This option allows you to change the relationship between the distance that "
"the mouse pointer moves on the screen and the relative movement of the "
"physical device itself (which may be a mouse, trackball, or some other "
"pointing device.)"
msgstr ""
"Aukera horrek saguaren erakuslea pantailan mugitzen den distantzia eta gailu "
"fisikoa beraren mugimendu erlatiboaren arteko erlazioa aldatzen uzten dizu "
"(sagu bat, kontrol-bola bat, edo beste gailu erakusleren bat izan "
"daitekeena)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Pointer speed"
msgid "Pointer acceleration"
msgstr "Erakuslearen abiadura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Standard</guilabel> mode adjusts the amount of pointer "
"acceleration according to how fast you move the mouse. If you set it to "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel>, the acceleration remains constant regardless of "
"speed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling: Invert scroll direction"
msgstr "Kiribiltzea: Alderantzikatu kiribiltze noranzkoa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this check box selected, the scroll wheel (if any) will work in the "
"opposite direction (so that if rolling the top of the scroll wheel towards "
"you previously causes a scroll down, then it will now cause a scroll up)."
msgstr ""
"Kontrol-lauki hau markatuta, kiribiltze-gurpila (egotekotan) aurkako "
"noranzkoan ibiliko da (horrela, kiribiltzeko gurpilaren goiko aldea zuregana "
"biratuz lehenago beherantz kiribiltzea eragiten badu, ondoren gorantz "
"kiribiltzea eragingo du)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &plasma; 5.13 you find the setting to use single or double mouse clicks "
"to open files and folders in the module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"workspaceoptions/index.html\">Workspace</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; 5.13an, fitxategiak eta karpetak klik bakar edo bikoitz batekin "
"irekitzeko ezarpena <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/workspaceoptions/index.html"
"\">Langunea</ulink> moduluan aurkitzen da."

#~ msgid "Acceleration profile"
#~ msgstr "Azelerazio-profila"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Adaptive</guilabel> profile is the default profile for all "
#~ "devices and takes the current speed of the device into account when "
#~ "deciding on acceleration. The <guilabel>Flat</guilabel> profile is simply "
#~ "a constant factor applied to all device deltas, regardless of the speed "
#~ "of motion."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Profil <guilabel>Moldakorra</guilabel> da gailu guztietarako profil "
#~ "lehenetsia eta, azelerazioari buruz erabakitzerakoan, gailuaren uneko "
#~ "abiadura kontuan hartzen du. Profil <guilabel>Laua</guilabel> gailuaren "
#~ "delta guztiei, mugimenduaren abiadura kontuan hartu gabe, aplikatutako "
#~ "faktore konstante bat besterik ez da."
